990\u5e74 \u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u5e74\u9593TOP100|publisher=Oricon|language=Japanese|accessdate=October 12, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331143622/http://www.geocities.jp/object_ori/1990a.html|archive-date=March 31, 2019|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|87\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|New Zealand (RMNZ)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/albums?chart=3879|title=Top Selling Albums of 1990|publisher=RIANZ|accessdate=October 12, 2015}}</ref>\n|28\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Norwegian Summer Period Albums (VG-lista)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lista.vg.no/liste/topp-40-album/2/dato/1990/periode/sommer|title=Topp 40 Album Sommer 1990|publisher=VG-lista|accessdate=October 12, 2015|language=Norwegian|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114232123/http://lista.vg.no/liste/topp-40-album/2/dato/1990/periode/sommer|archive-date=November 14, 2012|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|5\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|US ''Billboard'' 200<ref name=\"bilb1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.americanradiohistory.com/Archive-Billboard/90s/1990/Billboard-1990-12-22.pdf|title=1990 Year-end Charts|work=Billboard|accessdate=October 12, 2015}}</ref>\n|32\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|US Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums (''Billboard'')<ref name=\"bilb1\"/>\n|30\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|Chart (1991)\n!scope=\"col\"|Position\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Australian Albums (ARIA)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://aria.com.au/pages/aria-charts-end-of-year-charts-top-50albums-1991.htm|title=ARIA Charts - End Of Year Charts - Top 50 Albums 1991|publisher=ARIA|accessdate=October 12, 2015}}</ref>\n|6\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Canada Top Albums/CDs (''RPM'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?brws_s=1&file_num=nlc008388.1702&type=1&interval=24&PHPSESSID=mhe12pta2k83e08udtq66ot062|title=Top 100 Albums of 1991|work=RPM|accessdate=October 12, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408213817/http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?brws_s=1&file_num=nlc008388.1702&type=1&interval=24&PHPSESSI